title: Lee Child Jack Reacher Collection Books 1-5
description:
Lee Child's Jack Reacher Series

Jack Reacher is a drifter and ex-military policeman.

Each book in the series is a whole story with a beginning and an ending, and the plot of each book relies very little on the prior books in the series.


The following is the chronological order of the Jack Racher series:

This torrent contains 1-5

01 - Killing Floor - Dick Hill
02 - Die Trying - Dick Hill
03 - Tripwire - Garrick Hagon
04 - Running Blind - Dick Hill 
05 - Echo Burning - Jeff Harding 

06 - Without Fail - Dick Hill 
07 - Persuader - Dick Hill
08 - The Enemy - Jeff Harding
09 - One Shot - Jeff Harding
10 - The Hard Way - Dick Hill
11 - Bad Luck and Trouble - Dick Hill
12 - Nothing to Lose - Dick Hill
13 - Gone Tomorrow - Kerry Shale - Abridged
14 - 61 Hours - Dick Hill
15 - Worth Dying For - Dick Hill
16 - The Affair - Dick Hill
17 - A Wanted Man - Dick Hill - Unabridged

Only Book 17 is my rip.  My thanks to the original up-loaders.  I assume unabridged, but only know for certain on the one's I noted.
